tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    feedback_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_rating INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE review_analytics (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feedback_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    review_sentiment VARCHAR(50),
    review_analysis TEXT,
    review_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    review_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
